body.name: Personalized Kids Unicorn Stationery Set - Custom Journal - Notecards & Writing Paper - Inspirational Wall Art Print - Bujo - Watercolor Flowers For Girls - Gift
body.description: A personalized and custom notes set with an option to make it a complete stationery set. Also, makes a perfect gift for girls. *** Purchase the complete set and receive a FREE STATIONERY GIFT (may include pens, washi tape or stickers) *** - N O T E C A R D S - There are 8 hand-cut FLAT postcard style cards are approx. 4.25"x5.5", printed on heavy recycled eco white cardstock AND 8 sheets of coordinating paper approx. 5.5"x8.5"; printed on 28lb eco white writing paper. Kraft brown envelopes are included with an option to have them lined with coordinating printed liners. Our logo is printed on the bottom back of the card and paper. - J O U R N A L - The hand-crafted hardcover journal is approximately 6"x8.5" and includes blank or pre-printed pages, printed on 28lb. (105gsm) white paper. The back cover will have the same print with our logo at the bottom. Choose the type of pages you'd like for the inside. Options are blank, lined, and dotted (includes 120 pages). - 8 x 10 P R I N T - The personalized print is approx. 8"x10". Printed on hand-cut heavy cardstock. Choose between Glossy or Non-glossy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 5, 2022
reviews.reviewText: My daughter is really into sending letters to family members right now. I decided to get her this set for Christmas (I know.. it's only October). I could not be any happier. The quality is fantastic, the colors are beautiful, and it shipped quickly- even for a custom order! The packaging was wonderful as well. I will gladly buy my daughter this set again when she runs out!
